summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eighth Avenue Northeast from East Sixty-fifth Street to East Fifty-fifth Street produced in the City of Seattle, by laying water mains under Ordinance No. 15202, creating Local Improvement District No. 1389 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
